KI20160914.Rd

Pharmacokinetics of KI20160914 (Note that KI20160914 is a de-identified name for the drug.)

Usage

KI20160914_conc

KI20160914_dose

KI20160914_demog

Format

KI20160914_conc is concentration-time data for KI20160914. The data.frame has the following variables:

ID

Subject identifier

PERIOD

Period number for different visits in the study

TIME

Nominal time since first dose on DAY 1 in the current PERIOD (in hours)

TIME.FIRST.DOSE

Nominal time since first dose in PERIOD 1 (in hours)

DAY

Study day (since the beginning of PERIOD 1

CONC

Plasma concentration of KI20160914

FORMULATION

Formulation number

KI20160914_dose is dosing data. The data.frame has the following variables:

ID

Subject identifier

PERIOD

Period number for different visits in the study

TIME

Nominal time since first dose on DAY 1 in the current PERIOD (in hours)

TIME_FIRST_DOSE

Nominal time since first dose in PERIOD 1 (in hours)

TIMEU

Units for time, "hours"

DAY

Study day (since the beginning of PERIOD 1

DOSE

Dose of KI20160914 (in mg).

FORMULATION

Formulation number

ROUTE

Route of administration

KI20160914_demog is demographic data for KI20160914 pharmacokinetics. The data.frame has the following variables:

ID

Subject identifier

AGE

Subject's age (in years)

SEX

Subject's sex (Male/Female)

WEIGHT

Subject's body weight (in kg)
